  "title": "Sales Consultant",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Highlights:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Attractive Overall Salary Package (With Basic + Incentive + Sales Comms)</li>\n  <li>Provide systematic training (Both Theory &amp; Hands-on) related to TCM concept</li>\n  <li>Fun &amp; dynamic culture</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Job Scope:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Understand customers' needs and recommend suitable postpartum or aesthetic services</li>\n  <li>Promote the company’s services and products to potential and existing customers</li>\n  <li>Provide professional analysis and suggest suitable treatments and products</li>\n  <li>Deliver friendly and high-quality customer service before and after sales</li>\n  <li>Maintain high service standards and ensure treatment rooms are clean and tidy</li>\n  <li>Achieve and exceed individual and team sales targets</li>\n  <li>Stay updated on postpartum care, treatments, and industry trends</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Candidates without relevant experience are welcome to apply (training provided)</li>\n  <li>Candidate with relevant massage cert is a plus, not mandatory</li>\n  <li>Candidate may be required to work on weekends and retail hours</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></p>",
